Name: Lucy Red Dog Collar Size Small Color Red
Description:
Red leather dog collar in floral design that is perfect for girls. Reminiscent of warm sunny days, the Lucy collar is decorated with the delicate flowers of spring laying softly in an undulating pattern. Contrasting white stitching complete this beautiful design.

The backing leather is super soft Nappa leather to ensure your pup has the most comfortable and safe fit.

Features:

  • Perfect design for the girls.
  • Vegetable-dyed luxury top grain leather.
  • Buttery smooth texture with soft Nappa leather.
  • Super strong nickel branded buckle and D-ring.
  • Matching lead available.

NECK SIZES:

  • Medium (2.5cm/1") 34-38cm/13.5"-15"

Name: Moose Dog Toy
Description:
From the Canadian Rockies comes our moose toy.

With its lovable moose ears, cute face and big belly its the perfect play toy for your dog and will keep them happy for hours.

The toy is double-skinned for extra long life and made with tough canvas making it stronger and longer lasting to give your dog heaps of fun.

Plus there is the great sounding squeaker that will have them coming back to play for hours.

Size: 35cm long.

Name: Oodles and Curly Coat Dog Shampoo
Description:
Our unique Oodles, Poodles and curly coat shampoo is a naturally based gentle shampoo concentrate.

A great smelling, natural vanilla oil fragrance gives a deep, long-lasting freshness to the coat.

Specifically formulated with vitamins and oils that are essential for cleaning and maintaining oodles breeds and general curly coats.

Lanolin is used as a  deep cleanser and to help hold the hair strands together for curl retention. Pure Vitamin E is used for its antioxidant properties and it also promotes the circulation of blood to the skin & coat while natural Vitamin E oil is used as it benefits the coat by helping it retain its natural moisture content. Vitamin E oil also helps makes dull-looking and dry skin look healthier and fresher.

Made in Australia.

Key Features:

  • Natural Vanilla oil plant extracts.
  • Lanolin, Vitamin E oil, pure Vitamin E, natural proteins.
  • Concentrated formula, use only 30ml per 1 litre of water.
  • Contains a conditioning agent.
  • Formulated using pure deionised water.
  • Naturally based.
  • pH balanced.
  • Soap Free.
  • Free of phosphates, parabens, sulphate and enzymes.
  • Bio-degradable.
  • Animal cruelty-free - not tested on animals.

Description:
DESCRIPTION

Make your furry friend happy, set up a purr-fect feline home with our ergonomically built Cat Tree. Gives your cat a private, open, and safe area to exercise their hiss-terical rights! Which are - to play unconditionally, to enjoy unlimitedly, to juggle around dubiously, and to purr unavoidably. An intelligently aligned structure designed with ultimate perfection for convenience of jumping, climbing, or just simply hanging around. When they are done playing, they can comfort themselves on its soft and smooth surface Watch as they mark their territory in the most cutest way possible, a lovely memory for you to hold dear. Capture the most darnedest moments, share it with your friends and families. All of the fun your cat needs packed in one.

For extra durability and strength, it is made of high-quality MDF material. Equipped with steady and tough poles to withstand all the unpredictable maneuvers with ease. Crafted with a unique multi-level arrangement to expand the joy and amusement. The entire post is wrapped with natural sisal to tolerate paw scratches, complete freedom for your cat to express its instinct. The surface is covered with luxurious plush cover for a peaceful and relaxing experience. Ample space for you to hang toys, decorations, and many more.

Fur-real dangle, paw-some place to hang. Order your post now!

Key Features:

  • Perfect cat territory
  • Multi-level platform
  • Hanging toy
  • Natural sisal
  • Heavy-duty post

How to use a dog pad:
Unfold and place the pad, plastic side down, in a confined area, away from your dog's bed and food.
Place your dog on the pad several times so he can smell the pad and get used to it.
While your dog is eliminating on the pad, use a phrase like "go potty" so that eventually you can use the command and your dog will understand what it means.  
Immediately after the dog eliminates on the pad, reward him with praise and a treat.
If your dog has an accident, bring him back to the pad immediately. Continue bringing your dog back to the pad to reinforce that this is the place to go potty.
Dispose of soiled pads and replace as needed.To complete house training, gradually move the pad closer to the door and finally outside.
